OL,3,CInquest opens into death of Welsh
OL,4,CLabour MS Hefin David as family pay
OL,5,Ctribute
OL,7,FWelsh Labour politician Hefin David
OL,8,Fwas found dead at his home the day
OL,9,Fbefore his 48th birthday, the opening
OL,10,Fof an inquest into his death has heard.
OL,12,FMr David, 47, who had served as the
OL,13,FMember of the Senedd for Caerphilly
OL,14,Fsince 2016, was found dead in the
OL,15,FNelson area of Caerphilly on 12 August.
OL,17,FAn inquest into his death was opened
OL,18,Fat Gwent Coroner's Court on Tuesday,
OL,19,F26 August by area coroner Rose Farmer.
