OL,7,FMs Farmer said the cause of death was
OL,8,Funascertained pending toxicology. Mr
OL,9,FDavid was identified at the scene by
OL,10,Fhis sister.
OL,12,FAn inquest into his death will be held
OL,13,Fon April 7, 2026.
OL,15,FThe hearing was told that Mr David was
OL,16,Ffound hanged at his home address.
OL,18,FPolice were called to a report of a
OL,19,Fmedical emergency at an address in
OL,20,FNelson area of Caerphilly at around
OL,21,F6.55pm on 12 August.
