OL,7,FGwent Police previously said
OL,8,Fparamedics attended and confirmed that
OL,9,Fthe man had died.
OL,11,FIn a tribute, Mr David's family paid
OL,12,Ftribute to a "devoted father" and
OL,13,F"soulmate".
OL,15,FHis partner Vikki Howells is the MS
OL,16,Ffor Cynon Valley and minister for
OL,17,Ffurther and higher education in the
OL,18,FWelsh Government.
