OL,7,FIn a tribute shared by Welsh Labour,
OL,8,Fhis family said: "It is clear from the
OL,9,Fvery many messages we have received
OL,10,Fthat Hefin was widely respected and
OL,11,Fheld in genuine affection by the
OL,12,Fcommunity he represented, and by those
OL,13,Fhe worked with during his many years
OL,14,Fof public service.
