OL,7,F"But more than this, Hefin was a
OL,8,Fdevoted father who was adored by his
OL,9,Fdaughters Caitlin and Holly, a much-
OL,10,Floved son to Wynne and Christine, a
OL,11,Fbeloved brother to Sian, a brilliant
OL,12,Funcle to Osian and Catrin, and a
OL,13,Fsoulmate to his cherished partner
OL,14,FVikki.
OL,16,F"We are very grateful to all those who
OL,17,Fhave reached out to us since Hefin's
OL,18,Fpassing, and ask now for privacy to
OL,19,Fgrieve."
