OL,7,FThe Welsh Labour politician was first
OL,8,Felected as an MS for Caerphilly in
OL,9,F2016 and re-elected in 2021.
OL,11,FWales' First Minister Eluned Morgan
OL,12,Fsaid he was an "outstanding
OL,13,Fpolitician" and "much-loved member of
OL,14,Fthe Labour family", while Prime
OL,15,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer called Mr
OL,16,FDavid a "powerful voice for the people
OL,17,Fof Wales".
