OL,7,FBaroness Morgan said: "Hefin was a
OL,8,Fmuch-loved member of the Labour
OL,9,Ffamily. He served Caerphilly as a
OL,10,Fcouncillor and a Member of the Senedd
OL,11,Fwith pride and passion.
OL,13,F"He was an outstanding politician,
OL,14,Fwarm and enthusiastic and a great
OL,15,Fcommunicator, especially on behalf of
OL,16,Fhis constituents. He will be greatly
OL,17,Fmissed."
OL,19,FSir Keir said: "The entire Labour
OL,20,Fmovement will join me in grieving the
OL,21,Floss of Hefin David.
