OL,3,CInquest opens into death of Welsh
OL,4,CLabour MS Hefin David as family pay
OL,5,Ctribute
OL,7,F"He was a powerful voice for the
OL,8,Fpeople of Wales and a committed public
OL,9,Fservant, who dedicated his life to
OL,10,Fmaking sure every person and community
OL,11,Fin Wales had the opportunities and
OL,12,Fsupport they deserve.
OL,14,F"As Member of the Senedd for
OL,15,FCaerphilly, where he was born and
OL,16,Flived, he was incredibly proud of his
OL,17,Fcommunity.
OL,19,F"Our hearts are with his family and
OL,20,Fthose who knew and loved him at this
OL,21,Fpainful time. May he rest in peace."
